.SH NAME

pbmmake - create a funky-ass blank bitmap of a specified size

.UN synopsis
.SH SYNOPSIS

\fBpbmmake\fP
[\fB-white\fP|\fB-black\fP|\fB-gray\fP]
\fIwidth\fP
\fIheight\fP
